        "content": "## üö´ Mark received mail as read\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n* Vital control node for the Gmail trigger.\n* Marks the original incoming email as 'Read' after processing.\n* CRITICAL: Prevents infinite reply loops."
